Bahrain Withdraws From Hosting Formula One Race Because of Civil Unrest

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-02-21T15:50:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/bahrain-withdraws-from-hosting-formula-one-race-because-of-civil-unrest.html
Bahrain has withdrawn from hosting
the opening race of the Formula One motor racing season, the
Bahrain International Circuit said in an e-mailed statement
today.  Bahrain had been scheduled to host the race on March 13.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  